Yes!

93
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:26,200
Oh, sorry about that, I was busy with my studies.

94
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,840
Thank you so much, I'll send it asap.

95
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,880
[The bag doesn't have any defects, right? Why sell it so cheap?]

96
