Absolutely no defects. I wore it once and felt it didn't suit me,
so I wanted to sell it.

97
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:40,120
[Cool, thanks.]

98
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:52,000
Oh, dear Som... my sugar mama FC,

99
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,600
