107
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,120
You're a bad egg!

108
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:46,080
What do you want?

109
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,800
New car, huh?

110
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,440
Looks sharp.

111
