Or... you don't have one, do you?

114
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:03,400
Hey, are you okay?
You've been looking glum since morning.

115
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,280
Yeah, what’s wrong?

116
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,720
I ran into Ta yesterday.

117
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:15,760
Seemed like he wanted me to make love with me.

118
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,880
I cut it off and told him...

119
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,160
Tell what?

120
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:22,280
-I already got a partner.
-Huh...you got a partner?

121
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,920
Yep, and it's stressing me out.

122
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,040
Don't stress about it.

123
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:31,240
We just avoid places where he is,

124
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,600
