127
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,000
Look out, Ta's heading this way.

128
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,600
Hey there, Ta!

129
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,920
You've come a long way.

130
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:04,160
Actually, I have some business with Peem.

131
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,200
What is it?

132
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:22,400
