136
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,920
I’m dying to meet him.

137
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:49,280
Ink and Tide, make sure you come.

138
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,720
Alright.

139
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,120
Thanks.

140
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,160
See you there.

141
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:04,080
