151
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,400
What should I do then?

152
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,320
Can't be just any random person.

153
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:14,160
They have to match your stature.

154
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,400
Yeah,

155
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:19,400
