161
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:46,840
And with the party just 15 days away...

162
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,800
No worries, we've got 15 days.

163
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:52,600
Trust us, we'll help you out. There's gotta be someone.

164
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:53,840
Yeah,

165
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,120
I'm on it too.

166
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,320
Trust me.

167
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:59,720
There's gotta be a hidden gem here somewhere.

168
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,520
Let's grab a bite.

169
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:18,920
Is it good?

170
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,160
-Spicy.
-Aha.

171
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:23,560
-Drink some water.
-It's burning up.

172
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:38,800
Check out this guy.

173
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:42,240
Tall, Chinese-like and muscular.

174
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,440
