175
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,840
Pass.

176
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:58,520
What about this one?

177
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:01,160
I think he's as handsome as Ta.

178
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,040
Just handsome, huh?

179
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:07,600
I heard his family is going bankrupt.
Just skip!

180
