192
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:06,120
Oh? You mean Phol?

193
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:08,360
Yeah, Chaiphol.

194
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,480
Chaiphol? Who's that?

195
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:14,600
Chaiphol, real name Song-Itthiphol.

196
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,560
