Top student, ranked first in his faculty

201
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:35,680
But he's a bit strange, doesn’t like mingling with others.

202
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:39,360
I think Chaiphol is perfect for you, Peem.

203
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:45,200
