209
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:44,720
Maybe we need to be here as early as 5 AM to meet him.

210
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:48,960
Hmm, if it's earlier than this, count me out.
I can't wake up that early.

211
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,360
Gosh!

212
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,240
Hey, we’ve been waiting since 6 AM,

213
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,560
