218
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:51,080
Such a handsome guy, radiating a strong aura.

219
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,840
Guys, it’s him.

220
00:22:00,600 --> 00:22:02,600
Don’t just stand there stunned.
Let's follow him!

221
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:03,520
Hurry up!

222
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,120
Quickly!

223
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:12,800
I saw him.

224
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:14,200
Let’s go.

225
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:31,200
He’s rich, why eat in the cafeteria?

226
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:35,240
Maybe he’s just humble, not weird at all.

227
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:38,360
Wow... doesn't he care about anything else?

228
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:49,960
What a guy, why is he so perfect?

229
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:53,800
Doesn't he ever just chill out and have fun?

230
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:56,200
All he does is study. Must be pretty dull.

231
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,400
