232
00:23:58,800 --> 00:24:00,880
Come on, have some confidence!

233
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:04,360
You’re the star of the communications faculty, with lots of fans.

234
00:24:04,560 --> 00:24:05,920
A lot of people like you.

235
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:09,720
Trust me. If he meets you, he's bound to like you too.

236
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,440
Fight on, dude.

237
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:16,480
Shush!

238
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:18,640
Quiet, please. This is a library.

239
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:20,320
Sorry, ma'am.

240
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:51,120
How does he manage that? No social life. Boring!

241
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:53,360
He's just focused on his books.

242
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:56,520
Peem, you're running out of time.

243
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:58,200
Just give him a shot.

244
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:04,000
Today's the day—I'll tell him I like him.

245
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:14,360
Here he comes,

246
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,760
go for it!

247
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,360
Give him a shot.

248
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,800
Phol!

249
00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:26,680
I'm Peem.

250
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,360
Can I get your number?

251
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,440
Done talking?

252
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,080
What the heck was that?

253
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:50,720
What's with him? No social skills at all?

254
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:53,960
Peem, it’s okay.

255
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:18,440
Hey, you're late too.

256
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:21,080
Yeah, I couldn't sleep well last night.

257
00:26:22,360 --> 00:26:24,560
Worried about Phol, huh?

258
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:27,040
Don't worry about it.

259
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:30,320
I got something for you.

260
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,840
How did you manage to get this?

261
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:36,240
Traded my charm for it, obviously.

262
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:40,720
Thanks, my beautiful friend.

263
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:44,200
Relax, or you won't be able to focus in class.

264
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:46,120
Let's head in, we're already late.

265
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:20,880
